reviewText: If you're into the Goons you accept that the quality of the recordings from that era isn't good, which isn't helped by the low bitrate of these offerings, but with the BBC sourced shows going for up to 10 for 4 shows, to get the complete collection for this price is nothing short of a miracle. The unparalleled quality of Goon humour takes the value of this offering way over the Maximum I can award here.
